Temporally resample extracted GeoZarr data

Usage: eider resample [OPTIONS] <INPUT_DB> <OUTPUT_DB>

Arguments:
  <INPUT_DB>   The input DuckDB file containing the 'extracted_data' table
  <OUTPUT_DB>  The output DuckDB file to save the resampled data

Options:
      --freq <FREQ>      The temporal frequency (e.g., month, year, day)
      --agg <AGG>        The aggregate function to apply (e.g., avg, sum, max)
      --output <OUTPUT>  Output format (table or json) [possible values: table, json]
  -h, --help             Print help
